src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幸好的是黑寡婦本來就係佈景板所以影響不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟他們能否成功再一次阻止災難降臨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}